{"tid":505341,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視大鑊了】樂視香港申請清盤","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:50:37.000Z","uid":333,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8f44dbd314d8e58037d9143efacc7df985f50e","tid":505341,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"據法庭文件顯示，樂視香港已入紙申請清盤。<br />\n<br />\n內地網絡巨頭樂視自2015年攻港，在香港成立LeSports HK樂視體育。其後投得香港英超及NBA (於OTT平台) 等賽事之獨家播映權。不過，近期多次傳出資金鏈斷裂，今次樂視香港申請清盤，未知英超轉播權會否受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n今年11月，樂視體育出售世界盃播映權予電盈（0008）旗下的nowtv及viutv，至本月初則傳出樂視體育裁員200人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1513827983570&amp;issue=20171221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1513827983570%26issue%3D20171221&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZG%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6318c0eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1513827983570%26issue%3D20171221&h=2db4f19f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1513827983570&amp;issue=20171221</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食chips<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200662ec23ad8271f9489355ed80758cf44a1cdb","tid":505341,"uid":89037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a32fdedc93dfb73f07223d2b5c18eb0bca54125","tid":505341,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc464a939504f544605a12afa785bc1cc59abd56","tid":505341,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa